Part 6: Honeygain (Docker with amd64 emulation)
6.1 amd64 emulation enable
bash
# binfmt ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶ü‡¶Ü‡¶™ (multi-architecture support)
docker run --privileged --rm tonistiigi/binfmt --install amd64

# amd64 architecture ‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø extra libraries
sudo apt install -y qemu-user-static
6.2 Honeygain container ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®
bash
# Directory ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø
mkdir -p ~/docker/honeygain
cd ~/docker/honeygain

# docker-compose.yml ‡¶´‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶≤ ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø
nano docker-compose.yml
‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶∞ content ‡¶Ø‡ßã‡¶ó ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®:

yaml
version: "3.8"

services:
  honeygain:
    container_name: honeygain
    image: honeygain/honeygain:latest
    platform: linux/amd64
    environment:
      EMAIL: '‡¶Ü‡¶™‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞_‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶á‡¶≤'
      PASS: '‡¶Ü‡¶™‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞_‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶ì‡ßü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶°'
      DEVICE_NAME: 'raspberrypi-3b'
    networks:
      - pihole_network
    restart: unless-stopped
    deploy:
      resources:
        limits:
          cpus: '0.5'
          memory: 512M
        reservations:
          cpus: '0.25'
          memory: 256M
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "curl", "-f", "http://localhost:3000/"]
      interval: 60s
      timeout: 10s
      retries: 3

networks:
  pihole_network:
    external: true
6.3 Container ‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶≤‡ßÅ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶®
bash
docker compose up -d

# Status ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï
docker ps --filter "name=honeygain"

# Logs ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï
docker logs honeygain
Part 7: EarnApp (Native systemd service)
7.1 EarnApp ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶®
bash
